prompts.frontCover:
A humorous and lighthearted watercolor illustration for a birthday card front. The scene is a comically chaotic day at the beach. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan are depicted. Jordan is trying to put up a large, unwieldy beach umbrella that is being caught by a gust of wind, pulling him slightly off-balance with a look of funny determination. Lao Lao is laughing heartily beside him, holding two melting ice cream cones that are dripping onto the sand. A mischievous cartoon seagull is swooping down, wearing tiny sunglasses, about to snatch a chip from a bag near their beach blanket. The background is a bright, sunny beach with soft watercolor washes of turquoise water, gentle waves, and sandy-colored shores. A few other beach-goers are suggested in the far distance with simple, faded brush strokes.

In the center of the scene, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, lao lao!"
